<help>
.. class:: infomark

This tool requires files in *bed* format.

----

**What it does**
JAMM calls peaks on NGS data, i.e. for finding binding sites.

If you use it, please cite

 JAMM: A Peak Finder for Joint Analysis of NGS Replicates.
 
 Mahmoud M Ibrahim, Scott A Lacadie, Uwe Ohler 

</help>
</tool>
